- What?

13:38.240 --> 13:39.560
What time is it?

13:42.560 --> 13:43.560
Jesus...!

13:44.560 --> 13:47.560
- Hello?
- Pete.

13:47.560 --> 13:49.080
- Who's this?
- Evan.

13:49.080 --> 13:50.560
- Who?
- Who is it?

13:50.560 --> 13:52.560
You said I could call you.

13:52.560 --> 13:54.560
- Yeah, Evan, are you OK?
- No.

13:54.560 --> 13:55.560
No, I'm not.

13:57.560 --> 13:59.560
You do realise it's the middle of the night, mate?

13:59.560 --> 14:01.600
Yeah. That the worst time, isn't it?

14:04.560 --> 14:05.600
Yes.

14:05.600 --> 14:07.240
Yes, it is.

14:07.240 --> 14:08.560
Hang on a minute.

14:08.560 --> 14:10.560
I'll take this downstairs.

14:10.560 --> 14:11.560
I'm sorry, love.

14:13.560 --> 14:16.560
Are you all right, mate? Where are you? Are you safe?

14:18.560 --> 14:23.600
♪ And whispered In the sounds of silence. ♪

14:26.400 --> 14:27.760
David, you're so thoughtful.

14:27.760 --> 14:30.560
George never once bought me a new dress.

14:30.560 --> 14:32.560
Well, he gave me money so I could,

14:32.560 --> 14:35.600
but he'd have never known what suited me or fit me.

14:35.600 --> 14:37.560
You are clever.

14:38.560 --> 14:40.600
- Well, I had a bit of help.
- Oh?

14:49.560 --> 14:51.560
Er, excuse me.

14:51.560 --> 14:54.560
Erm, would you be willing to try this on for me?

14:54.560 --> 14:55.560
It's for my girlfriend.

14:55.560 --> 14:58.080
She's a similar, erm...

14:59.560 --> 15:01.560
..design to you.

15:02.560 --> 15:04.560
- OK.
- Oh, thank you.

15:04.560 --> 15:06.560
Thank you very much.

15:06.560 --> 15:07.560
She was very good about it.

15:07.560 --> 15:09.560
Tried on three dresses

15:09.560 --> 15:12.080
before we found the one that we thought was right.

15:12.080 --> 15:13.560
Who looks better in it?

15:16.560 --> 15:18.560
Wow...!

15:18.560 --> 15:19.560
I would.

15:20.560 --> 15:22.560
You do. By a country mile.

15:24.600 --> 15:28.240
- Would you like to choose the wine?
- You always do.

15:28.240 --> 15:30.560
Well, I have in the past, but since...

15:30.560 --> 15:32.560
David, nothing has changed.

15:32.560 --> 15:34.560
Just put it on the card and let's enjoy our evening.

15:36.560 --> 15:41.560
In that case, we'll have a bottle of the Montrachet Premier Cru. - 2012

15:41.560 --> 15:43.560
Certainly, sir.

